-- Copper Erases Decline in London, Trades Unchanged at $6,630 a Metric Ton
-- Dan Weeks
-- 2010-07-13T11:41:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/copper-erases-decline-in-london-trades-unchanged-at-6-630-a-metric-ton.html

          
          
             Copper for three-month delivery
erased a drop of as much as 1.1 percent on the London Metal
Exchange and traded unchanged at $6,630 a metric ton.  
          
          


  


        